var book = {
	"name": "Hosea",
	"numChapters": 14,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> that came<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22096A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22096A\"></sup> to Hosea son of Beeri during the reigns of Uzziah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22096B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22096B\"></sup> Jotham,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22096C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22096C\"></sup> Ahaz<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22096D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22096D\"></sup> and Hezekiah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22096E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22096E\"></sup> kings of Judah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22096F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22096F\"></sup> and during the reign of Jeroboam<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22096G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22096G\"></sup> son of Jehoash king of Israel:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22096H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22096H\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> began to speak through Hosea, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to him, “Go, marry a promiscuous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22097I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22097I\"></sup> woman and have children with her, for like an adulterous wife this land is guilty of unfaithfulness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22097J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22097J\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>So he married Gomer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22098K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22098K\"></sup> daughter of Diblaim, and she conceived and bore him a son.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Hosea, “Call him Jezreel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22099L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22099L\"></sup> because I will soon punish the house of Jehu for the massacre at Jezreel, and I will put an end to the kingdom of Israel.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>In that day I will break Israel’s bow in the Valley of Jezreel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22100M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22100M\"></sup>”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Gomer<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22101N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22101N\"></sup> conceived again and gave birth to a daughter. Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to Hosea, “Call her Lo-Ruhamah (which means “not loved”),<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22101O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22101O\"></sup> for I will no longer show love to Israel,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22101P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22101P\"></sup> that I should at all forgive them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Yet I will show love to Judah; and I will save them—not by bow,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22102Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22102Q\"></sup> sword or battle, or by horses and horsemen, but I, the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22102R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22102R\"></sup> will save them.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>After she had weaned Lo-Ruhamah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22103S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22103S\"></sup> Gomer had another son.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said, “Call him Lo-Ammi (which means “not my people”), for you are not my people, and I am not your God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22104T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22104T\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Yet the Israelites will be like the sand on the seashore, which cannot be measured or counted.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22105U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22105U\"></sup> In the place where it was said to them, ‘You are not my people,’ they will be called ‘children of the living God.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22105V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22105V\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The people of Judah and the people of Israel will come together;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22106W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22106W\"></sup> they will appoint one leader<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22106X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22106X\"></sup> and will come up out of the land,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22106Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22106Y\"></sup> for great will be the day of Jezreel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22106Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22106Z\"></sup>"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>“Say of your brothers, ‘My people,’ and of your sisters, ‘My loved one.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22107A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22107A\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Rebuke your mother,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22108B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22108B\"></sup> rebuke her,for she is not my wife,and I am not her husband.Let her remove the adulterous<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22108C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22108C\"></sup> look from her faceand the unfaithfulness from between her breasts.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Otherwise I will strip<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22109D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22109D\"></sup> her nakedand make her as bare as on the day she was born;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22109E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22109E\"></sup>I will make her like a desert,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22109F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22109F\"></sup>turn her into a parched land,and slay her with thirst.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I will not show my love to her children,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22110G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22110G\"></sup>because they are the children of adultery.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22110H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22110H\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Their mother has been unfaithfuland has conceived them in disgrace.She said, ‘I will go after my lovers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22111I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22111I\"></sup>who give me my food and my water,my wool and my linen, my olive oil and my drink.’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22111J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22111J\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Therefore I will block her path with thornbushes;I will wall her in so that she cannot find her way.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22112K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22112K\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>She will chase after her lovers but not catch them;she will look for them but not find them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22113L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22113L\"></sup>Then she will say,‘I will go back to my husband<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22113M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22113M\"></sup> as at first,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22113N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22113N\"></sup>for then I was better off<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22113O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22113O\"></sup> than now.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>She has not acknowledged<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22114P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22114P\"></sup> that I was the onewho gave her the grain, the new wine and oil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22114Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22114Q\"></sup>who lavished on her the silver and gold<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22114R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22114R\"></sup>—which they used for Baal.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22114S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22114S\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Therefore I will take away my grain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22115T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22115T\"></sup> when it ripens,and my new wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22115U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22115U\"></sup> when it is ready.I will take back my wool and my linen,intended to cover her naked body.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>So now I will expose<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22116V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22116V\"></sup> her lewdnessbefore the eyes of her lovers;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22116W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22116W\"></sup>no one will take her out of my hands.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22116X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22116X\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I will stop<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22117Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22117Y\"></sup> all her celebrations:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22117Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22117Z\"></sup>her yearly festivals, her New Moons,her Sabbath days—all her appointed festivals.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22117AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22117AA\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I will ruin her vines<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22118AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22118AB\"></sup> and her fig trees,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22118AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22118AC\"></sup>which she said were her pay from her lovers;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22118AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22118AD\"></sup>I will make them a thicket,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22118AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22118AE\"></sup>and wild animals will devour them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22118AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22118AF\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I will punish her for the daysshe burned incense<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22119AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22119AG\"></sup> to the Baals;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22119AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22119AH\"></sup>she decked herself with rings and jewelry,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22119AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22119AI\"></sup>and went after her lovers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22119AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22119AJ\"></sup>but me she forgot,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22119AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22119AK\"></sup>”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22119AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22119AL\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“Therefore I am now going to allure her;I will lead her into the wilderness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22120AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22120AM\"></sup>and speak tenderly to her.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>There I will give her back her vineyards,and will make the Valley of Achor<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22121AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22121AN\"></sup> a door of hope.There she will respond<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22121AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22121AO\"></sup> as in the days of her youth,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22121AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22121AP\"></sup>as in the day she came up out of Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22121AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22121AQ\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“In that day,” declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,“you will call me ‘my husband’;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22122AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22122AR\"></sup>you will no longer call me ‘my master.’",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>I will remove the names of the Baals from her lips;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22123AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22123AS\"></sup>no longer will their names be invoked.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22123AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22123AT\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>In that day I will make a covenant for themwith the beasts of the field, the birds in the skyand the creatures that move along the ground.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22124AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22124AU\"></sup>Bow and sword and battleI will abolish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22124AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22124AV\"></sup> from the land,so that all may lie down in safety.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22124AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22124AW\"></sup>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>I will betroth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22125AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22125AX\"></sup> you to me forever;I will betroth you in righteousness and justice,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22125AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22125AY\"></sup>in love and compassion.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22125AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22125AZ\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>I will betroth you in faithfulness,and you will acknowledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22126BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22126BA\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22126BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22126BB\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“In that day I will respond,”declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>—“I will respond<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22127BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22127BC\"></sup> to the skies,and they will respond to the earth;",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>and the earth will respond to the grain,the new wine and the olive oil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22128BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22128BD\"></sup>and they will respond to Jezreel.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22128BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22128BE\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>I will plant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22129BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22129BF\"></sup> her for myself in the land;I will show my love to the one I called ‘Not my loved one.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22129BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22129BG\"></sup>’I will say to those called ‘Not my people,’ ‘You are my people’;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22129BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22129BH\"></sup>and they will say, ‘You are my God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22129BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22129BI\"></sup>’”"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> said to me, “Go, show your love to your wife again, though she is loved by another man and is an adulteress.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22130A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22130A\"></sup> Love her as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> loves the Israelites, though they turn to other gods and love the sacred raisin cakes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22130B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22130B\"></sup>”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>So I bought her for fifteen shekels of silver and about a homer and a lethek of barley.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then I told her, “You are to live with me many days; you must not be a prostitute or be intimate with any man, and I will behave the same way toward you.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For the Israelites will live many days without king or prince,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22133C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22133C\"></sup> without sacrifice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22133D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22133D\"></sup> or sacred stones,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22133E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22133E\"></sup> without ephod<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22133F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22133F\"></sup> or household gods.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22133G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22133G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Afterward the Israelites will return and seek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22134H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22134H\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> their God and David their king.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22134I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22134I\"></sup> They will come trembling<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22134J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22134J\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> and to his blessings in the last days.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22134K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22134K\"></sup>"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Hear the word of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>, you Israelites,because the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has a charge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22135A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22135A\"></sup> to bringagainst you who live in the land:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22135B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22135B\"></sup>“There is no faithfulness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22135C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22135C\"></sup> no love,no acknowledgment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22135D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22135D\"></sup> of God in the land.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22135E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22135E\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>There is only cursing, lying<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22136F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22136F\"></sup> and murder,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22136G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22136G\"></sup>stealing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22136H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22136H\"></sup> and adultery;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22136I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22136I\"></sup>they break all bounds,and bloodshed follows bloodshed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22136J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22136J\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Because of this the land dries up,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22137K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22137K\"></sup>and all who live in it waste away;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22137L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22137L\"></sup>the beasts of the field, the birds in the skyand the fish in the sea are swept away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22137M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22137M\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“But let no one bring a charge,let no one accuse another,for your people are like thosewho bring charges against a priest.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22138N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22138N\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You stumble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22139O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22139O\"></sup> day and night,and the prophets stumble with you.So I will destroy your mother<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22139P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22139P\"></sup>—",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>my people are destroyed from lack of knowledge.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22140Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22140Q\"></sup>“Because you have rejected knowledge,I also reject you as my priests;because you have ignored the law<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22140R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22140R\"></sup> of your God,I also will ignore your children.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The more priests there were,the more they sinned against me;they exchanged their glorious God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22141S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22141S\"></sup> for something disgraceful.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22141T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22141T\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>They feed on the sins of my peopleand relish their wickedness.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22142U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22142U\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And it will be: Like people, like priests.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22143V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22143V\"></sup>I will punish both of them for their waysand repay them for their deeds.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22143W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22143W\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“They will eat but not have enough;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22144X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22144X\"></sup>they will engage in prostitution<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22144Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22144Y\"></sup> but not flourish,because they have deserted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22144Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22144Z\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>to give themselves",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum mid-line\">11 </sup>to prostitution;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22145AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22145AA\"></sup>old wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22145AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22145AB\"></sup> and new winetake away their understanding.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22145AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22145AC\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>My people consult a wooden idol,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22146AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22146AD\"></sup>and a diviner’s rod speaks to them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22146AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22146AE\"></sup>A spirit of prostitution<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22146AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22146AF\"></sup> leads them astray;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22146AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22146AG\"></sup>they are unfaithful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22146AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22146AH\"></sup> to their God.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>They sacrifice on the mountaintopsand burn offerings on the hills,under oak,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22147AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22147AI\"></sup> poplar and terebinth,where the shade is pleasant.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22147AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22147AJ\"></sup>Therefore your daughters turn to prostitution<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22147AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22147AK\"></sup>and your daughters-in-law to adultery.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22147AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22147AL\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“I will not punish your daughterswhen they turn to prostitution,nor your daughters-in-lawwhen they commit adultery,because the men themselves consort with harlots<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22148AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22148AM\"></sup>and sacrifice with shrine prostitutes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22148AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22148AN\"></sup>—a people without understanding<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22148AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22148AO\"></sup> will come to ruin!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22148AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22148AP\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Though you, Israel, commit adultery,do not let Judah become guilty.“Do not go to Gilgal;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22149AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22149AQ\"></sup>do not go up to Beth Aven.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22149AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22149AR\"></sup>And do not swear, ‘As surely as the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> lives!’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22149AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22149AS\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The Israelites are stubborn,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22150AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22150AT\"></sup>like a stubborn heifer.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22150AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22150AU\"></sup>How then can the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> pasture themlike lambs<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22150AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22150AV\"></sup> in a meadow?",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Ephraim is joined to idols;leave him alone!",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Even when their drinks are gone,they continue their prostitution;their rulers dearly love shameful ways.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>A whirlwind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22153AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22153AW\"></sup> will sweep them away,and their sacrifices will bring them shame.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22153AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22153AX\"></sup>"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>“Hear this, you priests!Pay attention, you Israelites!Listen, royal house!This judgment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22154A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22154A\"></sup> is against you:You have been a snare<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22154B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22154B\"></sup> at Mizpah,a net<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22154C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22154C\"></sup> spread out on Tabor.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The rebels are knee-deep in slaughter.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22155D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22155D\"></sup>I will discipline all of them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22155E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22155E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I know all about Ephraim;Israel is not hidden<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22156F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22156F\"></sup> from me.Ephraim, you have now turned to prostitution;Israel is corrupt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22156G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22156G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Their deeds do not permit themto return<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22157H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22157H\"></sup> to their God.A spirit of prostitution<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22157I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22157I\"></sup> is in their heart;they do not acknowledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22157J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22157J\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Israel’s arrogance testifies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22158K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22158K\"></sup> against them;the Israelites, even Ephraim, stumble<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22158L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22158L\"></sup> in their sin;Judah also stumbles with them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22158M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22158M\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>When they go with their flocks and herdsto seek the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22159N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22159N\"></sup>they will not find him;he has withdrawn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22159O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22159O\"></sup> himself from them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>They are unfaithful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22160P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22160P\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;they give birth to illegitimate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22160Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22160Q\"></sup> children.When they celebrate their New Moon feasts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22160R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22160R\"></sup>he will devour<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22160S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22160S\"></sup> their fields.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Sound the trumpet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22161T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22161T\"></sup> in Gibeah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22161U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22161U\"></sup>the horn in Ramah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22161V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22161V\"></sup>Raise the battle cry in Beth Aven;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22161W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22161W\"></sup>lead on, Benjamin.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Ephraim will be laid waste<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22162X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22162X\"></sup>on the day of reckoning.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22162Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22162Y\"></sup>Among the tribes of IsraelI proclaim what is certain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22162Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22162Z\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Judah’s leaders are like thosewho move boundary stones.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22163AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22163AA\"></sup>I will pour out my wrath<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22163AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22163AB\"></sup> on themlike a flood of water.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Ephraim is oppressed,trampled in judgment,intent on pursuing idols.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22164AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22164AC\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I am like a moth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22165AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22165AD\"></sup> to Ephraim,like rot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22165AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22165AE\"></sup> to the people of Judah.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“When Ephraim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22166AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22166AF\"></sup> saw his sickness,and Judah his sores,then Ephraim turned to Assyria,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22166AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22166AG\"></sup>and sent to the great king for help.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22166AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22166AH\"></sup>But he is not able to cure<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22166AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22166AI\"></sup> you,not able to heal your sores.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22166AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22166AJ\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For I will be like a lion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22167AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22167AK\"></sup> to Ephraim,like a great lion to Judah.I will tear them to pieces<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22167AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22167AL\"></sup> and go away;I will carry them off, with no one to rescue them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22167AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22167AM\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then I will return to my lair<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22168AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22168AN\"></sup>until they have borne their guilt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22168AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22168AO\"></sup>and seek my face<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22168AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22168AP\"></sup>—in their misery<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22168AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22168AQ\"></sup>they will earnestly seek me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22168AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22168AR\"></sup>”"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>“Come, let us return<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22169A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22169A\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.He has torn us to pieces<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22169B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22169B\"></sup>but he will heal us;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22169C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22169C\"></sup>he has injured usbut he will bind up our wounds.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22169D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22169D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>After two days he will revive us;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22170E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22170E\"></sup>on the third day<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22170F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22170F\"></sup> he will restore<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22170G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22170G\"></sup> us,that we may live in his presence.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Let us acknowledge the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;let us press on to acknowledge him.As surely as the sun rises,he will appear;he will come to us like the winter rains,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22171H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22171H\"></sup>like the spring rains that water the earth.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22171I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22171I\"></sup>”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“What can I do with you, Ephraim?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22172J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22172J\"></sup>What can I do with you, Judah?Your love is like the morning mist,like the early dew that disappears.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22172K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22172K\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Therefore I cut you in pieces with my prophets,I killed you with the words of my mouth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22173L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22173L\"></sup>—then my judgments go forth like the sun.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22173M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22173M\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For I desire mercy, not sacrifice,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22174N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22174N\"></sup>and acknowledgment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22174O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22174O\"></sup> of God rather than burnt offerings.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22174P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22174P\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>As at Adam, they have broken the covenant;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22175Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22175Q\"></sup>they were unfaithful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22175R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22175R\"></sup> to me there.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Gilead is a city of evildoers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22176S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22176S\"></sup>stained with footprints of blood.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>As marauders lie in ambush for a victim,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22177T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22177T\"></sup>so do bands of priests;they murder<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22177U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22177U\"></sup> on the road to Shechem,carrying out their wicked schemes.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22177V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22177V\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I have seen a horrible<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22178W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22178W\"></sup> thing in Israel:There Ephraim is given to prostitution,Israel is defiled.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22178X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22178X\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Also for you, Judah,a harvest<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22179Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22179Y\"></sup> is appointed.“Whenever I would restore the fortunes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22179Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22179Z\"></sup> of my people,"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span><sup class=\"versenum mid-line\">1 </sup>whenever I would heal Israel,the sins of Ephraim are exposedand the crimes of Samaria revealed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22180A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22180A\"></sup>They practice deceit,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22180B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22180B\"></sup>thieves break into houses,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22180C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22180C\"></sup>bandits rob in the streets;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22180D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22180D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>but they do not realizethat I remember<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22181E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22181E\"></sup> all their evil deeds.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22181F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22181F\"></sup>Their sins engulf them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22181G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22181G\"></sup>they are always before me.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“They delight the king with their wickedness,the princes with their lies.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22182H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22182H\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They are all adulterers,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22183I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22183I\"></sup>burning like an ovenwhose fire the baker need not stirfrom the kneading of the dough till it rises.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>On the day of the festival of our kingthe princes become inflamed with wine,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22184J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22184J\"></sup>and he joins hands with the mockers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22184K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22184K\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Their hearts are like an oven;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22185L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22185L\"></sup>they approach him with intrigue.Their passion smolders all night;in the morning it blazes like a flaming fire.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>All of them are hot as an oven;they devour their rulers.All their kings fall,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22186M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22186M\"></sup>and none of them calls<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22186N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22186N\"></sup> on me.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Ephraim mixes<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22187O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22187O\"></sup> with the nations;Ephraim is a flat loaf not turned over.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Foreigners sap his strength,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22188P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22188P\"></sup>but he does not realize it.His hair is sprinkled with gray,but he does not notice.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Israel’s arrogance testifies against him,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22189Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22189Q\"></sup>but despite all thishe does not return<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22189R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22189R\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> his Godor search<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22189S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22189S\"></sup> for him.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Ephraim is like a dove,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22190T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22190T\"></sup>easily deceived and senseless—now calling to Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22190U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22190U\"></sup>now turning to Assyria.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22190V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22190V\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When they go, I will throw my net<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22191W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22191W\"></sup> over them;I will pull them down like the birds in the sky.When I hear them flocking together,I will catch them.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Woe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22192X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22192X\"></sup> to them,because they have strayed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22192Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22192Y\"></sup> from me!Destruction to them,because they have rebelled against me!I long to redeem thembut they speak about me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22192Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22192Z\"></sup> falsely.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22192AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22192AA\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>They do not cry out to me from their hearts<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22193AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22193AB\"></sup>but wail on their beds.They slash themselves, appealing to their godsfor grain and new wine,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22193AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22193AC\"></sup>but they turn away from me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22193AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22193AD\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>I trained<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22194AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22194AE\"></sup> them and strengthened their arms,but they plot evil<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22194AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22194AF\"></sup> against me.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>They do not turn to the Most High;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22195AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22195AG\"></sup>they are like a faulty bow.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22195AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22195AH\"></sup>Their leaders will fall by the swordbecause of their insolent<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22195AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22195AI\"></sup> words.For this they will be ridiculed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22195AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22195AJ\"></sup>in the land of Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22195AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22195AK\"></sup>"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>“Put the trumpet<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22196A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22196A\"></sup> to your lips!An eagle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22196B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22196B\"></sup> is over the house of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>because the people have broken my covenant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22196C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22196C\"></sup>and rebelled against my law.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22196D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22196D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Israel cries out to me,‘Our God, we acknowledge you!’",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But Israel has rejected what is good;an enemy will pursue him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22198E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22198E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They set up kings without my consent;they choose princes without my approval.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22199F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22199F\"></sup>With their silver and goldthey make idols<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22199G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22199G\"></sup> for themselvesto their own destruction.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Samaria, throw out your calf-idol!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22200H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22200H\"></sup>My anger burns against them.How long will they be incapable of purity?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22200I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22200I\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>They are from Israel!This calf—a metalworker has made it;it is not God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22201J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22201J\"></sup>It will be broken in pieces,that calf<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22201K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22201K\"></sup> of Samaria.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22201L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22201L\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“They sow the windand reap the whirlwind.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22202M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22202M\"></sup>The stalk has no head;it will produce no flour.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22202N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22202N\"></sup>Were it to yield grain,foreigners would swallow it up.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22202O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22202O\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Israel is swallowed up;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22203P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22203P\"></sup>now she is among the nationslike something no one wants.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22203Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22203Q\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For they have gone up to Assyria<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22204R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22204R\"></sup>like a wild donkey<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22204S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22204S\"></sup> wandering alone.Ephraim has sold herself to lovers.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22204T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22204T\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Although they have sold themselves among the nations,I will now gather them together.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22205U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22205U\"></sup>They will begin to waste away<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22205V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22205V\"></sup>under the oppression of the mighty king.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Though Ephraim built many altars for sin offerings,these have become altars for sinning.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22206W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22206W\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>I wrote for them the many things of my law,but they regarded them as something foreign.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22207X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22207X\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Though they offer sacrifices as gifts to me,and though they eat<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22208Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22208Y\"></sup> the meat,the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is not pleased with them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22208Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22208Z\"></sup>Now he will remember<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22208AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22208AA\"></sup> their wickednessand punish their sins:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22208AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22208AB\"></sup>They will return to Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22208AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22208AC\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Israel has forgotten<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22209AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22209AD\"></sup> their Maker<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22209AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22209AE\"></sup>and built palaces;Judah has fortified many towns.But I will send fire on their citiesthat will consume their fortresses.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22209AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22209AF\"></sup>"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>Do not rejoice, Israel;do not be jubilant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22210A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22210A\"></sup> like the other nations.For you have been unfaithful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22210B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22210B\"></sup> to your God;you love the wages of a prostitute<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22210C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22210C\"></sup>at every threshing floor.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Threshing floors and winepresses will not feed the people;the new wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22211D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22211D\"></sup> will fail them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>They will not remain<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22212E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22212E\"></sup> in the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>’s land;Ephraim will return to Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22212F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22212F\"></sup>and eat unclean food in Assyria.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22212G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22212G\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They will not pour out wine offerings<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22213H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22213H\"></sup> to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,nor will their sacrifices please<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22213I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22213I\"></sup> him.Such sacrifices will be to them like the bread of mourners;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22213J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22213J\"></sup>all who eat them will be unclean.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22213K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22213K\"></sup>This food will be for themselves;it will not come into the temple of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22213L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22213L\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>What will you do<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22214M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22214M\"></sup> on the day of your appointed festivals,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22214N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22214N\"></sup>on the feast days of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>?",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Even if they escape from destruction,Egypt will gather them,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22215O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22215O\"></sup>and Memphis<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22215P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22215P\"></sup> will bury them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22215Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22215Q\"></sup>Their treasures of silver<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22215R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22215R\"></sup> will be taken over by briers,and thorns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22215S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22215S\"></sup> will overrun their tents.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The days of punishment<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22216T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22216T\"></sup> are coming,the days of reckoning<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22216U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22216U\"></sup> are at hand.Let Israel know this.Because your sins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22216V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22216V\"></sup> are so manyand your hostility so great,the prophet is considered a fool,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22216W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22216W\"></sup>the inspired person a maniac.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22216X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22216X\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The prophet, along with my God,is the watchman over Ephraim,yet snares<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22217Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22217Y\"></sup> await him on all his paths,and hostility in the house of his God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22217Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22217Z\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>They have sunk deep into corruption,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22218AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22218AA\"></sup>as in the days of Gibeah.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22218AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22218AB\"></sup>God will remember<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22218AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22218AC\"></sup> their wickednessand punish them for their sins.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22218AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22218AD\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“When I found Israel,it was like finding grapes in the desert;when I saw your ancestors,it was like seeing the early fruit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22219AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22219AE\"></sup> on the fig<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22219AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22219AF\"></sup> tree.But when they came to Baal Peor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22219AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22219AG\"></sup>they consecrated themselves to that shameful idol<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22219AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22219AH\"></sup>and became as vile as the thing they loved.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Ephraim’s glory<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22220AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22220AI\"></sup> will fly away like a bird<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22220AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22220AJ\"></sup>—no birth, no pregnancy, no conception.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22220AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22220AK\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Even if they rear children,I will bereave<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22221AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22221AL\"></sup> them of every one.Woe<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22221AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22221AM\"></sup> to themwhen I turn away from them!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22221AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22221AN\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I have seen Ephraim,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22222AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22222AO\"></sup> like Tyre,planted in a pleasant place.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22222AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22222AP\"></sup>But Ephraim will bring outtheir children to the slayer.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22222AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22222AQ\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Give them, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>—what will you give them?Give them wombs that miscarryand breasts that are dry.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22223AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22223AR\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Because of all their wickedness in Gilgal,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22224AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22224AS\"></sup>I hated them there.Because of their sinful deeds,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22224AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22224AT\"></sup>I will drive them out of my house.I will no longer love them;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22224AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22224AU\"></sup>all their leaders are rebellious.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22224AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22224AV\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Ephraim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22225AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22225AW\"></sup> is blighted,their root is withered,they yield no fruit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22225AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22225AX\"></sup>Even if they bear children,I will slay<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22225AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22225AY\"></sup> their cherished offspring.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>My God will reject<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22226AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22226AZ\"></sup> thembecause they have not obeyed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22226BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22226BA\"></sup> him;they will be wanderers among the nations.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22226BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22226BB\"></sup>"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>Israel was a spreading vine;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22227A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22227A\"></sup>he brought forth fruit for himself.As his fruit increased,he built more altars;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22227B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22227B\"></sup>as his land prospered,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22227C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22227C\"></sup>he adorned his sacred stones.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22227D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22227D\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Their heart is deceitful,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22228E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22228E\"></sup>and now they must bear their guilt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22228F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22228F\"></sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will demolish their altars<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22228G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22228G\"></sup>and destroy their sacred stones.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22228H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22228H\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then they will say, “We have no kingbecause we did not revere the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.But even if we had a king,what could he do for us?”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They make many promises,take false oaths<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22230I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22230I\"></sup>and make agreements;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22230J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22230J\"></sup>therefore lawsuits spring uplike poisonous weeds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22230K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22230K\"></sup> in a plowed field.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The people who live in Samaria fearfor the calf-idol<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22231L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22231L\"></sup> of Beth Aven.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22231M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22231M\"></sup>Its people will mourn over it,and so will its idolatrous priests,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22231N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22231N\"></sup>those who had rejoiced over its splendor,because it is taken from them into exile.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22231O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22231O\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>It will be carried to Assyria<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22232P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22232P\"></sup>as tribute<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22232Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22232Q\"></sup> for the great king.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22232R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22232R\"></sup>Ephraim will be disgraced;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22232S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22232S\"></sup>Israel will be ashamed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22232T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22232T\"></sup> of its foreign alliances.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Samaria’s king will be destroyed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22233U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22233U\"></sup>swept away like a twig on the surface of the waters.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The high places<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22234V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22234V\"></sup> of wickedness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22234W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22234W\"></sup> will be destroyed—it is the sin of Israel.Thorns<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22234X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22234X\"></sup> and thistles will grow upand cover their altars.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22234Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22234Y\"></sup>Then they will say to the mountains, “Cover us!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22234Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22234Z\"></sup>and to the hills, “Fall on us!”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22234AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22234AA\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Since the days of Gibeah,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22235AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22235AB\"></sup> you have sinned,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22235AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22235AC\"></sup> Israel,and there you have remained.Will not war again overtakethe evildoers in Gibeah?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When I please, I will punish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22236AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22236AD\"></sup> them;nations will be gathered against themto put them in bonds for their double sin.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Ephraim is a trained heiferthat loves to thresh;so I will put a yoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22237AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22237AE\"></sup>on her fair neck.I will drive Ephraim,Judah must plow,and Jacob must break up the ground.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Sow<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22238AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22238AF\"></sup> righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22238AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22238AG\"></sup> for yourselves,reap the fruit of unfailing love,and break up your unplowed ground;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22238AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22238AH\"></sup>for it is time to seek<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22238AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22238AI\"></sup> the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>,until he comesand showers his righteousness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22238AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22238AJ\"></sup> on you.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But you have planted wickedness,you have reaped evil,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22239AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22239AK\"></sup>you have eaten the fruit of deception.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22239AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22239AL\"></sup>Because you have depended on your own strengthand on your many warriors,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22239AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22239AM\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>the roar of battle will rise against your people,so that all your fortresses will be devastated<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22240AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22240AN\"></sup>—as Shalman<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22240AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22240AO\"></sup> devastated Beth Arbel on the day of battle,when mothers were dashed to the ground with their children.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22240AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22240AP\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So will it happen to you, Bethel,because your wickedness is great.When that day dawns,the king of Israel will be completely destroyed.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22241AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22241AQ\"></sup>"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>“When Israel was a child,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22242A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22242A\"></sup> I loved<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22242B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22242B\"></sup> him,and out of Egypt I called my son.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22242C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22242C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>But the more they were called,the more they went away from me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22243D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22243D\"></sup>They sacrificed to the Baals<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22243E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22243E\"></sup>and they burned incense to images.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22243F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22243F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>It was I who taught Ephraim to walk,taking them by the arms;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22244G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22244G\"></sup>but they did not realizeit was I who healed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22244H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22244H\"></sup> them.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I led them with cords of human kindness,with ties of love.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22245I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22245I\"></sup>To them I was like one who liftsa little child to the cheek,and I bent down to feed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22245J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22245J\"></sup> them.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22245K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22245K\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Will they not return to Egypt<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22246L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22246L\"></sup>and will not Assyria<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22246M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22246M\"></sup> rule over thembecause they refuse to repent?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22246N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22246N\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>A sword<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22247O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22247O\"></sup> will flash in their cities;it will devour<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22247P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22247P\"></sup> their false prophetsand put an end to their plans.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>My people are determined to turn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22248Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22248Q\"></sup> from me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22248R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22248R\"></sup>Even though they call me God Most High,I will by no means exalt them.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“How can I give you up,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22249S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22249S\"></sup> Ephraim?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22249T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22249T\"></sup>How can I hand you over, Israel?How can I treat you like Admah?How can I make you like Zeboyim?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22249U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22249U\"></sup>My heart is changed within me;all my compassion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22249V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22249V\"></sup> is aroused.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22249W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22249W\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I will not carry out my fierce anger,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22250X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22250X\"></sup>nor will I devastate<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22250Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22250Y\"></sup> Ephraim again.For I am God, and not a man<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22250Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22250Z\"></sup>—the Holy One<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22250AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22250AA\"></sup> among you.I will not come against their cities.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They will follow the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>;he will roar<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22251AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22251AB\"></sup> like a lion.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22251AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22251AC\"></sup>When he roars,his children will come trembling<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22251AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22251AD\"></sup> from the west.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22251AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22251AE\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>They will come from Egypt,trembling like sparrows,from Assyria,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22252AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22252AF\"></sup> fluttering like doves.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22252AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22252AG\"></sup>I will settle them in their homes,”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22252AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22252AH\"></sup>declares the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Ephraim has surrounded me with lies,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22253AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22253AI\"></sup>Israel with deceit.And Judah is unruly against God,even against the faithful<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22253AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22253AJ\"></sup> Holy One.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22253AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22253AK\"></sup>"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span><sup class=\"versenum mid-line\">1 </sup>Ephraim<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22254A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22254A\"></sup> feeds on the wind;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22254B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22254B\"></sup>he pursues the east wind all dayand multiplies lies and violence.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22254C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22254C\"></sup>He makes a treaty with Assyria<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22254D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22254D\"></sup>and sends olive oil to Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22254E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22254E\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> has a charge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22255F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22255F\"></sup> to bring against Judah;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22255G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22255G\"></sup>he will punish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22255H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22255H\"></sup> Jacob according to his waysand repay him according to his deeds.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22255I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22255I\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>In the womb he grasped his brother’s heel;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22256J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22256J\"></sup>as a man he struggled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22256K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22256K\"></sup> with God.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>He struggled with the angel and overcame him;he wept and begged for his favor.He found him at Bethel<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22257L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22257L\"></sup>and talked with him there—",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> God Almighty,the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> is his name!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22258M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22258M\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But you must return<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22259N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22259N\"></sup> to your God;maintain love and justice,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22259O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22259O\"></sup>and wait for your God always.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22259P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22259P\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The merchant uses dishonest scales<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22260Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22260Q\"></sup>and loves to defraud.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Ephraim boasts,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22261R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22261R\"></sup>“I am very rich; I have become wealthy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22261S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22261S\"></sup>With all my wealth they will not find in meany iniquity or sin.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“I have been the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your Godever since you came out of Egypt;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22262T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22262T\"></sup>I will make you live in tents<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22262U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22262U\"></sup> again,as in the days of your appointed festivals.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>I spoke to the prophets,gave them many visionsand told parables<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22263V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22263V\"></sup> through them.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22263W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22263W\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Is Gilead wicked?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22264X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22264X\"></sup>Its people are worthless!Do they sacrifice bulls in Gilgal?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22264Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22264Y\"></sup>Their altars will be like piles of stoneson a plowed field.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22264Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22264Z\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Jacob fled to the country of Aram;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22265AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22265AA\"></sup>Israel served to get a wife,and to pay for her he tended sheep.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22265AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22265AB\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>The <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> used a prophet to bring Israel up from Egypt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22266AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22266AC\"></sup>by a prophet he cared for him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22266AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22266AD\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But Ephraim has aroused his bitter anger;his Lord will leave on him the guilt of his bloodshed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22267AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22267AE\"></sup>and will repay him for his contempt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22267AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22267AF\"></sup>"
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>When Ephraim spoke, people trembled;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22268A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22268A\"></sup>he was exalted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22268B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22268B\"></sup> in Israel.But he became guilty of Baal worship<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22268C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22268C\"></sup> and died.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Now they sin more and more;they make<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22269D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22269D\"></sup> idols for themselves from their silver,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22269E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22269E\"></sup>cleverly fashioned images,all of them the work of craftsmen.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22269F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22269F\"></sup>It is said of these people,“They offer human sacrifices!They kiss<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22269G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22269G\"></sup> calf-idols!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22269H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22269H\"></sup>”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Therefore they will be like the morning mist,like the early dew that disappears,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22270I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22270I\"></sup>like chaff<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22270J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22270J\"></sup> swirling from a threshing floor,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22270K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22270K\"></sup>like smoke<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22270L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22270L\"></sup> escaping through a window.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“But I have been the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your Godever since you came out of Egypt.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22271M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22271M\"></sup>You shall acknowledge<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22271N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22271N\"></sup> no God but me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22271O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22271O\"></sup>no Savior<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22271P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22271P\"></sup> except me.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I cared for you in the wilderness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22272Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22272Q\"></sup>in the land of burning heat.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>When I fed them, they were satisfied;when they were satisfied, they became proud;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22273R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22273R\"></sup>then they forgot<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22273S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22273S\"></sup> me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22273T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22273T\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>So I will be like a lion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22274U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22274U\"></sup> to them,like a leopard I will lurk by the path.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Like a bear robbed of her cubs,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22275V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22275V\"></sup>I will attack them and rip them open;like a lion<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22275W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22275W\"></sup> I will devour them—a wild animal will tear them apart.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22275X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22275X\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“You are destroyed, Israel,because you are against me,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22276Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22276Y\"></sup> against your helper.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22276Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22276Z\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Where is your king,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22277AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22277AA\"></sup> that he may save you?Where are your rulers in all your towns,of whom you said,‘Give me a king and princes’?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22277AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22277AB\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>So in my anger I gave you a king,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22278AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22278AC\"></sup>and in my wrath I took him away.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22278AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22278AD\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The guilt of Ephraim is stored up,his sins are kept on record.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22279AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22279AE\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Pains as of a woman in childbirth<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22280AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22280AF\"></sup> come to him,but he is a child without wisdom;when the time<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22280AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22280AG\"></sup> arrives,he doesn’t have the sense to come out of the womb.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22280AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22280AH\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“I will deliver this people from the power of the grave;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22281AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22281AI\"></sup>I will redeem them from death.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22281AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22281AJ\"></sup>Where, O death, are your plagues?Where, O grave, is your destruction?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22281AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22281AK\"></sup>“I will have no compassion,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>even though he thrives<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22282AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22282AL\"></sup> among his brothers.An east wind<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22282AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22282AM\"></sup> from the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> will come,blowing in from the desert;his spring will failand his well dry up.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22282AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22282AN\"></sup>His storehouse will be plundered<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22282AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22282AO\"></sup>of all its treasures.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The people of Samaria<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22283AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22283AP\"></sup> must bear their guilt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22283AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22283AQ\"></sup>because they have rebelled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22283AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22283AR\"></sup> against their God.They will fall by the sword;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22283AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22283AS\"></sup>their little ones will be dashed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22283AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22283AT\"></sup> to the ground,their pregnant women<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22283AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22283AU\"></sup> ripped open.”"
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>Return,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22284A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22284A\"></sup> Israel, to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> your God.Your sins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22284B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22284B\"></sup> have been your downfall!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22284C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22284C\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Take words with youand return to the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span>.Say to him:“Forgive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22285D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22285D\"></sup> all our sinsand receive us graciously,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22285E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22285E\"></sup>that we may offer the fruit of our lips.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22285F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22285F\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Assyria cannot save us;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22286G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22286G\"></sup>we will not mount warhorses.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22286H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22286H\"></sup>We will never again say ‘Our gods’<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22286I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22286I\"></sup>to what our own hands have made,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22286J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22286J\"></sup>for in you the fatherless<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22286K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22286K\"></sup> find compassion.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“I will heal<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22287L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22287L\"></sup> their waywardness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22287M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22287M\"></sup>and love them freely,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22287N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22287N\"></sup>for my anger has turned away<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22287O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22287O\"></sup> from them.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>I will be like the dew<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22288P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22288P\"></sup> to Israel;he will blossom like a lily.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22288Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22288Q\"></sup>Like a cedar of Lebanon<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22288R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22288R\"></sup>he will send down his roots;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22288S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22288S\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>his young shoots will grow.His splendor will be like an olive tree,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22289T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22289T\"></sup>his fragrance like a cedar of Lebanon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22289U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22289U\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>People will dwell again in his shade;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22290V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22290V\"></sup>they will flourish like the grain,they will blossom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22290W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22290W\"></sup> like the vine—Israel’s fame will be like the wine<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22290X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22290X\"></sup> of Lebanon.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22290Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22290Y\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Ephraim, what more have I to do with idols?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22291Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22291Z\"></sup>I will answer him and care for him.I am like a flourishing juniper;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22291AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22291AA\"></sup>your fruitfulness comes from me.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Who is wise?<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22292AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22292AB\"></sup> Let them realize these things.Who is discerning? Let them understand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22292AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22292AC\"></sup>The ways of the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Lord</span> are right;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22292AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22292AD\"></sup>the righteous walk<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-22292AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-22292AE\"></sup> in them,but the rebellious stumble in them."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;